# Citation File Format (CFF) for Sensory Tracer Science
# This file provides standardized citation information for academic use

cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
type: software

title: "Sensory Tracer Science: Physics-Based Framework for Sensory Analysis"
abstract: >
  A rigorous physics-based framework for sensory tracer analysis with complete 
  biological realism, quantum mechanical compliance, and thermodynamic consistency.
  The framework implements five fundamental axioms governing sensory information 
  propagation while respecting energy conservation (Landauer's Principle), 
  information conservation (Shannon's Theory), causality (relativistic limits), 
  quantum constraints (Heisenberg Uncertainty), and biological limits (ATP energetics).

